Package: NPS
Type: Package
Title: "NPS -- Adopting tipping-point theory to transcriptome profiles to unravel disease regulatory trajectory."
Version: 0.99.0
Author: Zhezhen Wang and Biniam Feleke 
Maintainer: Zhezhen Wang <zhezhen@uchicago.edu>
Description: Contains functions for classifying transcript biotypes and finding long transcripts that overlap more than two coding regions.
